flowchart TD
    Start([User Action: Update Progress]) --> ActionType{Goal Type?}
    ActionType -->|Quantitative| QtyInput[User enters new currentValue]
    ActionType -->|Qualitative| QualInput[User updates status/rating]
    ActionType -->|Binary| BinInput[User checks/unchecks item]
    ActionType -->|Milestone| MilInput[User completes milestone]
    ActionType -->|Recurring| RecInput[User marks occurrence complete]
    ActionType -->|Habit| HabInput[User marks day complete]
    
    QtyInput --> Capture[UI Component: Capture Input]
    QualInput --> Capture
    BinInput --> Capture
    MilInput --> Capture
    RecInput --> Capture
    HabInput --> Capture
    
    Capture --> ValidateInput{Validate input client-side}
    ValidateInput -->|Invalid| ShowError[Show error]
    ShowError --> UserFixes[User fixes]
    UserFixes --> ValidateInput
    ValidateInput -->|Valid| Optimistic[Optimistic Update]
    
    Optimistic --> DispatchPending[Dispatch: updateProgressPending]
    DispatchPending --> UpdateStore[Update goal in store immediately]
    UpdateStore --> ShowLoading[Show loading state]
    ShowLoading --> CalcService[Progress Calculation Service]
    
    CalcService --> CalcType{Goal Type?}
    CalcType -->|Quantitative| CalcQty[progress = current - start / target - start * 100]
    CalcType -->|Milestone| CalcMil[progress = completedMilestones / totalMilestones * 100]
    CalcType -->|Binary| CalcBin[progress = currentCount / targetCount * 100]
    CalcType -->|Qualitative| CalcQual[progress = status-based or rating-based]
    CalcType -->|Recurring| CalcRec[progress = completedOccurrences / totalOccurrences * 100]
    CalcType -->|Habit| CalcHab[progress = completedDays / totalDays * 100]
    
    CalcQty --> Clamp[Clamp progress: 0-100 or allow >100]
    CalcMil --> Clamp
    CalcBin --> Clamp
    CalcQual --> Clamp
    CalcRec --> Clamp
    CalcHab --> Clamp
    
    Clamp --> ReturnCalc[Return: progress, isComplete, message]
    ReturnCalc --> APIService[API Service: updateProgress]
    APIService --> PrepareRequest[Prepare request: goalId, progress, progressEntry, type-specific updates]
    PrepareRequest --> HTTPRequest[HTTP Request: PATCH /api/goals/:id/progress]
    HTTPRequest --> Backend[Backend API Handler]
    Backend --> LoadGoal[Load goal from database]
    LoadGoal --> ValidateUpdate{Validate update}
    ValidateUpdate --> CheckPerms[Check user permissions]
    CheckPerms --> ValidateProgress[Validate progress value 0-100]
    ValidateProgress --> ValidateType[Validate type-specific fields]
    ValidateType --> CheckDeps{Has dependencies?}
    CheckDeps -->|Yes| ValidateDeps[Check dependencies for milestones]
    ValidateDeps --> Recalc[Recalculate progress server-side validation]
    CheckDeps -->|No| Recalc
    Recalc --> CreateHistory[Create progress history entry]
    CreateHistory --> UpdateGoal[Update goal: progress, currentValue/currentCount/etc., updatedAt, progressHistory]
    UpdateGoal --> CheckComplete{Progress = 100%?}
    CheckComplete -->|Yes| SuggestComplete[Suggest completion]
    CheckComplete -->|No| SaveDB
    SuggestComplete --> SaveDB[Database: UPDATE Goal + INSERT ProgressEntry]
    SaveDB --> Transaction[Transaction: UPDATE goals SET progress=?, currentValue=?, updatedAt=?]
    Transaction --> InsertHistory[INSERT INTO progress_history]
    InsertHistory --> ReturnUpdated[Return: Updated goal]
    ReturnUpdated --> APIResponse[API Response: 200 OK]
    APIResponse --> TransformResponse[API Service: Transform Response]
    TransformResponse --> UpdateStore2[State Management: Update Store]
    UpdateStore2 --> DispatchSuccess[Dispatch: updateProgressSuccess]
    DispatchSuccess --> ReplaceOptimistic[Replace optimistic update with real data]
    ReplaceOptimistic --> UpdateGoalStore[Update goal in store]
    UpdateGoalStore --> UpdateCache[Update goal list cache if applicable]
    UpdateCache --> UpdateUI[UI Component: Update View]
    UpdateUI --> UpdateProgressBar[Update progress bar: progress%]
    UpdateProgressBar --> UpdatePercentage[Update progress percentage display]
    UpdatePercentage --> AddHistory[Add entry to progress history timeline]
    AddHistory --> UpdateTypeDisplay{Update type-specific displays}
    UpdateTypeDisplay -->|Quantitative| ShowQty[currentValue, progress bar]
    UpdateTypeDisplay -->|Milestone| ShowMil[Steps component, milestone status]
    UpdateTypeDisplay -->|Recurring/Habit| ShowRec[Calendar heatmap, streak]
    ShowQty --> ShowSuccess[Show success message optional]
    ShowMil --> ShowSuccess
    ShowRec --> ShowSuccess
    ShowSuccess --> End([Progress Updated Successfully])

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style End fill:#c8e6c9
    style ActionType fill:#fff9c4
    style ValidateInput fill:#fff9c4
    style CalcType fill:#fff9c4
    style ValidateUpdate fill:#fff9c4
    style CheckDeps fill:#fff9c4
    style CheckComplete fill:#fff9c4
    style UpdateTypeDisplay fill:#fff9c4

